data.description: Must see this gorgeous Craftsman-inspired home with the largest floor plan in the neighborhood! Kitchen with large island, lots of cabinet space, granite counters, walk-in pantry, open to the family room with built in bookshelves, gas fire place with opens to a private fenced patio! Features a separate dining room and private study. Large master’s suite with two closets and bath with dual vanities, separate soaking tub and tile shower. Second floor includes a loft area and two more spacious bedrooms share a Jack & Jill bath. The third floor can be a guest suite with it own bath!Lawn maintenance is included in the HOA. Walk to restaurants, shopping and entertainment!
